  "text": "C is a shared layer taking the image as the input, and F C is a shared fully-connected layer for classification [CITATION_1] . B R k is a block, composed of a serial of convolutional layers. B L k is an identity layer, or a convolutional layer that exists only when the corresponding block in the deep base network contains a down-scale operation. Deep fusion combines the blocks across 2 base networks:",
